# ===================================================
# Gmail SMTP Configuration for Contact Form
# ===================================================
# 
# IMPORTANT: You MUST use a Gmail App Password, NOT your regular Gmail password!
# Regular passwords will NOT work with Gmail SMTP.
#
# How to Generate a Gmail App Password:
# --------------------------------------
# 1. Visit: https://myaccount.google.com/security
# 2. Under "How you sign in to Google", enable "2-Step Verification" (if not already enabled)
# 3. After enabling 2-Step Verification, go back to the Security page
# 4. Scroll down and click on "App passwords" (sous "2-Step Verification")
# 5. You may need to sign in again
# 6. In the "Select app" dropdown, choose "Mail"
# 7. In the "Select device" dropdown, choose "Other (Custom name)"
# 8. Type "Portfolio Contact Form" as the name
# 9. Click "Generate"
# 10. Copy the 16-character password (format: xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx)
# 11. Paste it below WITHOUT spaces
#
# Example:
# GMAIL_USER=blkfatine2@gmail.com
# GMAIL_PASSWORD=abcdefghijklmnop (16 characters, no spaces)
#
# ===================================================

GMAIL_USER=blkfatine2@gmail.com
GMAIL_PASSWORD=your-16-character-app-password-here
